Necrofurs
[[Image:LateGuest.jpg|thumb|your mum can sure draw huh?]]
Necrofurs are the bastard spawn of [[Necrophiliacs]] and [[Furfags]]. They have been persecuted by everyone in the known universe since [[last thursday]], and known Necrofurs include Karavan, Mathias Blackwolf, [[Michael Jackson]] and [[your mum]].


==Typical Necrofur Behaviour==

Necrofurs are a weird bunch indeed. They are torn between two sick, sick fetishes, namely being [[Michael Jackson|corpses]] and [[Nigra|anthropomorphic animals]]. This is truly a terrifying prospect for everyone, and has been the source of much [[anti-lulz]] in both the [[necrophiliac]] (because, as everyone knows, fucking animals is [[Michael Jackson| wrong]]) and [[furry]] (because as everyone knows, fucking dead people is wrong) communities. Both have furvently denied the existence of necrofurs, and state that the Necrofur is the furry/necro equivalent of the [[Michael Jackson| boogie man]].

As they have been rejected by both their parent families, Necrofurs tend to be pretty damn [[emo|warped individuals]], who have the capacity to say/do/fuck pretty random shit.
Necrofurs tend to live in the a/h board of [[fchan]]. If you're lucky enough not to know anything about the cesspit of [[faggotry]], then I shall briefly say the the a/h board is the place where the darkest, most deeply disturbing furry fetishes go to wallow in their own self depredation. 
Take for example Matthias Blackwolf. Not only is Matthias Blackwolf a Necrofur, but he also creates necrofur [[shit|artwork]] to feed his underlings with. 


